{
  "stem": "268.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "In those days, when the Germans first-- first built Buchenwald, they also built a movie theater for because that was sort of a show camp and for most political prisoners, German political prisoners, communists.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "So they built that-- built a movie-- a regular movie theater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "They were showing all kind of propaganda movies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But by the time that Buchenwald got to be so overpopulated, they converted it into living and-- and cooking quarters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "So we would line up in front of the so-called theater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And once a day, we sat maybe in line two or three hours a day before you got your daily soup and two or three potatoes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And-- and you just constantly hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- how can I get out of Buchenwald?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I heard someone say they looking for volunteers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They looking for-- for what they call [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[GERMAN] in German means trades-- tradespeople and that that particular call was for-- for electricians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was not an electrician.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never had the opportunity to learn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I worked with-- with-- you know, on construction with some electricians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember, I used to hand them different-- different tools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of them was a-- a-- a-- a-- [GERMAN], I remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a-- what, like a big scissors, a tool that would bend pipes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And little did I know that this one tool may save my life again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything is small miracles, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as they called for a tradesman, I-- I-- I had enough courage to-- to line up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm also a tradesman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm an electrician.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no idea what-- I-- all I-- all I did is helping hand a tool to a real electrician on the construction.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was up there on a ladder.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
